CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776186394
OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FThe US military says it will begin a
OL,7,Fblockade of all Iranian ports and
OL,8,Fcoastal areas on Monday, tempering
OL,9,FPresident Trump's earlier vow to
OL,10,Fentirely block the strategic Strait of
OL,11,FHormuz.
OL,13,FThe blockade, which US Central Command
OL,14,F(CENTCOM) said would be "enforced
OL,15,Fimpartially against vessels of all
OL,16,Fnations", is due to begin at 10am EDT,
OL,17,For 3pm UK time.
OL,19,FThe move comes after marathon US-Iran
OL,20,Fceasefire talks in Pakistan ended
OL,21,Fwithout reaching an agreement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
