PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776186394
OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FSpeaking late Sunday, President Donald
OL,7,FTrump told reporters that he is "fine"
OL,8,Fif Iran doesn't return to negotiations.
OL,10,F"I don't care if they come back or
OL,11,Fnot. If they don't come back, I'm
OL,12,Ffine", he said, adding that the
OL,13,Fceasefire is "holding well".
OL,15,FWriting on his Truth Social platform,
OL,16,FTrump said that "other countries will
OL,17,Fbe involved with this blockade",
OL,18,Fwithout elaborating further, but it is
OL,19,Funderstood that the UK will not
OL,20,Fparticipate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
