FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776186394
OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FBlockade could further rattle global
OL,7,Fenergy markets
OL,9,FIn its statement, CENTCOM said the
OL,10,Fblockade would include all Iranian
OL,11,Fports. But, it said, it would still
OL,12,Fallow ships travelling between non-
OL,13,FIranian ports to transit the vital
OL,14,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,16,FThe blockage is likely intended to add
OL,17,Fpressure on Iran, which has exported
OL,18,Fmillions of barrels of oil since the
OL,19,Fwar began - much of it likely carried
OL,20,Fby so-called "dark" transits that
OL,21,Fevade Western sanctions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776186394
OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FThe announcement of the blockade
OL,7,Fhalted the limited ship traffic that
OL,8,Fresumed in the strait since the
OL,9,Fceasefire, said an early report from
OL,10,FLloyd's List intelligence.
OL,12,FMarine trackers say over 40 commercial
OL,13,Fships have crossed since the start of
OL,14,Fthe ceasefire, down from roughly 100
OL,15,Fto 135 vessel passages per day before
OL,16,Fthe war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
