FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776186394
OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FTrump also hopes to undercut Iran's
OL,7,Fcontrol over the Strait of Hormuz
OL,8,Fafter demanding that it reopen the
OL,9,Fwaterway, through which much of the
OL,10,Fworld's oil passed before the war. A
OL,11,FUS blockade could further rattle
OL,12,Fglobal energy markets.
OL,14,FOil prices rose once again in early
OL,15,Fmarket trading since the blockade
OL,16,Fannouncement, with the benchmark
OL,17,Finternational standard Brent crude
OL,18,Frising 7% to $102.29 a barrel. Brent
OL,19,Fcrude cost roughly $70 a barrel before
OL,20,Fthe beginning of the war, in late
OL,21,FFebruary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
