OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FPeace talks end without agreement
OL,8,FThe announcement came after the
OL,9,Fpresident said he would "immediately"
OL,10,Fbegin blockading the region after
OL,11,Fpeace talks in Pakistan ended without
OL,12,Fan agreement.
OL,14,FThe president said he has "instructed
OL,15,Four Navy to seek and interdict every
OL,16,Fvessel in International Waters that
OL,17,Fhas paid a toll to Iran. No one who
OL,18,Fpays an illegal toll will have safe
OL,19,Fpassage on the high seas."
OL,26,@vD@[OU{D@ZO]
