OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FTrump also said the US was ready to
OL,7,F"finish up" Iran at the "appropriate
OL,8,Fmoment," stressing that Tehran's
OL,9,Fnuclear ambitions were at the core of
OL,10,Fthe failure to end the war.
OL,12,FVice President JD Vance, who led the
OL,13,FUS delegation during the 21 hours of
OL,14,Ftalks in Pakistan's capital,
OL,15,FIslamabad, said negotiations finished
OL,16,Fwithout a deal after the Iranians
OL,17,Frefused to accept American terms to
OL,18,Frefrain from developing a nuclear
OL,19,Fweapon, something one Iranian official
OL,20,Fdenied.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@KO]oD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
