OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FSpeaking on Sunday, Iran's Foreign
OL,7,FMinistry said negotiations fell apart
OL,8,Fover a "gap between our opinions over
OL,9,Ftwo or three important issues."
OL,11,F"Ultimately, the talks didn't result
OL,12,Fin an agreement," spokesperson Esmaeil
OL,13,FBaghaei told Iran's state TV. He did
OL,14,Fnot detail what those issues were.
OL,16,FOn Sunday, a chorus of top-ranking
OL,17,FIranian officials threatened
OL,18,Fretaliation to Trump's announcement of
OL,19,Fa blockade.
OL,26,@pD@HOUqD@_O]sD@AOUtD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
