PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776186394
OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FMohsen Rezaei, a military adviser and
OL,7,Fa former Revolutionary Guard
OL,8,FCommander, wrote on X that the
OL,9,Fcountry's armed forces had "major
OL,10,Funtouched levers" to counter a Hormuz
OL,11,Fblockade. He said Iran would not be
OL,12,Fcoerced by "tweets and imaginary
OL,13,Fplans."
OL,15,FIran's parliament speaker, Mohammad
OL,16,FBagher Qalibaf, who led Iran's side in
OL,17,Fthe talks, addressed Trump in a
OL,18,Fstatement on his return to Iran: "If
OL,19,Fyou fight, we will fight".
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@QO]tD@LOUuD@GO]
