OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FKeir Starmer refuses to join Hormuz
OL,7,Fblockade
OL,9,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,10,Frefused to join Donald Trump's
OL,11,Fblockade of the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,12,Fwhich could compound economic pain for
OL,13,FBritons with higher petrol costs.
OL,15,FThe UK is "urgently working with
OL,16,FFrance and other partners to put
OL,17,Ftogether a wide coalition to protect
OL,18,Ffreedom of navigation," a government
OL,19,Fspokesperson said.
OL,26,@wD@KOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
