OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FTrump told Fox News "the UK and a
OL,7,Fcouple of other countries are sending
OL,8,Fmine sweepers" to the strait, and "it
OL,9,Fwon't take long to clean it out".
OL,11,FStarmer previously said UK mine
OL,12,Fhunting systems were already in the
OL,13,Fregio, but this is thought to refer to
OL,14,Fminesweeping drones which could be
OL,15,Fdeployed once the situation
OL,16,Fstabilises, and to be distinct from
OL,17,FTrump's blockade.
