OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FThe prime minister is due to discuss
OL,7,Fcost-of-living pressures with local
OL,8,Fpeople on a visit to Greater
OL,9,FManchester on Monday, while Chancellor
OL,10,FRachel Reeves will travel to
OL,11,FWashington for International Monetary
OL,12,FFund meetings this week.
OL,14,FTwo-week ceasefire agreement continues
OL,16,FThe face-to-face talks on Saturday
OL,17,Fcame a few days after a fragile
OL,18,Fceasefire was announced as the war
OL,19,Fthat has killed thousands of people
OL,20,Fand shaken global markets entered its
OL,21,Fseventh week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
