OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FIran's foreign minister claimed that
OL,7,Fthe U.S. tanked the negotiations when
OL,8,Fthey were within "inches" of an
OL,9,Fagreement, but did not provide
OL,10,Fevidence.
OL,12,F"We encountered maximalism, shifting
OL,13,Fgoalposts, and blockade," wrote Abbas
OL,14,FAraghchi on X.
OL,16,FNeither Iran nor the U.S. indicated
OL,17,Fwhat will happen after the ceasefire
OL,18,Fexpires on April 22.
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@YO]uD@YO]
