OL,3,CUS to blockade ports, as Trump says he
OL,4,C'doesn't care' if Iran returns to talks
OL,6,FTrump has also renewed his war-of-
OL,7,Fwords with Pope Leo XIV, who
OL,8,Fpreviously criticised the president's
OL,9,Frhetoric regarding the conflict.
OL,11,FIn a post on Truth Social early on
OL,12,FMonday, Trump said: "Pope Leo is WEAK
OL,13,Fon Crime, and terrible for Foreign
OL,14,FPolicy... I don't want a Pope who
OL,15,Fthinks it's OK for Iran to have a
OL,16,FNuclear Weapon."
OL,18,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
